---
const bannerImage =
  "/img/privileges/entrance.jpg";
---

<section class="bg-[#FBFBFA] px-5 pb-10 pt-10 md:px-10 md:pb-14 lg:px-12" aria-labelledby="projects-cta-title">
  <div class="oc-media-fallback relative isolate min-h-[18rem] overflow-hidden border border-slate-900/10 bg-[#F5F4F0] md:min-h-[20rem]">
    <img
      src={bannerImage}
      alt="Архитектурная лестница и озеленение в жилом комплексе"
      width="1800"
      height="1000"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover saturate-[0.9] contrast-[1.03]"
      onerror="this.dataset.failed='true'"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(251,251,250,0.96)_0%,rgba(251,251,250,0.88)_32%,rgba(251,251,250,0.32)_62%,rgba(15,23,42,0.18)_100%)]"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 grid max-w-[34rem] gap-5 p-5 md:p-10 lg:p-12">
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase leading-relaxed tracking-[0.18em] text-violet-700">
        Консультация
      </p>
      <h2 id="projects-cta-title" class="text-3xl font-medium uppercase leading-[0.96] tracking-normal text-slate-950 md:text-5xl">
        Поможем выбрать идеальный объект.
      </h2>
      <p class="max-w-[30rem] text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 md:text-base">
        Ответим на вопросы по объектам, срокам и доступным форматам покупки, чтобы сузить выбор без лишнего давления.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/#contact"
        class="group mt-2 inline-grid w-fit max-w-full grid-cols-[1fr_auto] items-center bg-slate-950 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase leading-none tracking-[0.14em] text-[#FBFBFA] transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-violet-700 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-4 focus-visible:outline-violet-700"
      >
        <span class="px-5 py-4">Получить консультацию</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="grid h-full min-w-12 place-items-center border-l border-[#FBFBFA]/20 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-0.5">
          →
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
